## diffModules() function

> This API is provided as an alpha preview for developers and may change based on feedback that we receive. Do not use this API in a production environment.
> 

Compares two module analyses and produces API changes.

Requires TypeChecker for accurate semantic analysis. Use `parseModuleWithTypes()` to create the input analyses.

**Signature:**

```typescript
export declare function diffModules(oldAnalysis: ModuleAnalysisWithTypes, newAnalysis: ModuleAnalysisWithTypes, options?: DiffOptions): ApiChange[];
```
